{"tid":2350794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[共諜現身] 愛立信CEO威脅瑞典商務部：馬上解除華為禁令，遭瑞典政府堅決拒絕","createTime":"2021-01-02T15:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T08:46:42.000Z","uid":155095,"like":232,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8aa473e1767010d02c8cd14d0f43fdc8dcb764","tid":2350794,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3399579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3399579&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb02aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=f75b863e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3399579&h=921f0676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3399579</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞典封殺中國華為及中興通訊參與5G網路建設，瑞典通訊大廠愛立信（Ericsson）CEO完全不挺。根據Pledge times引述瑞典《Dagens Nyheter》消息稱，愛立信CEO Borje Ekholm 寫了短信給瑞典商務部長，威脅除非解除對華為和中興的禁令，否則該公司不排除離開瑞典。商務部長則以「無法干預政府決定」強硬回絕。<br />\n<br />\n愛立信CEO Borje Ekholm 在短信中稱：「我仍然希望得到瑞典的幫助，以及我們在這個國家的存在能夠獲得重視。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6eCF5w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6eCF5w.png&h=aed199b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商務部長Anna Hallberg則以「無法干預政府的決定」強硬回應，Anna Hallberg解釋，因為這一決定是由瑞典PTS（Police and Telecommunications Administration）根據安全部門和國防部門的建議作出的。<br />\n<br />\nBorje Ekholm又寫到：「嗨，Anna，我感謝您所做的工作，但現在看來，瑞典對愛立信來說是一個非常糟糕的國家。」<br />\n<br />\nAnna Hallberg 則向愛立信保證，「瑞典非常重視愛立信，但也會保持瑞典作為世界上最自由貿易國家之一的地位。」這一回應，沒想到又換來Borje Ekholm斥責，「當你處於我們的位置，你會完全明白為什麼歐洲的科技公司如此之少。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.bld.news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/shutterstock_1629403723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.bld.news%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fshutterstock_1629403723.jpg&h=dfffa312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，去年10月，瑞典PTS宣布禁止華為及中興通訊參與瑞典5G建設後，在華為提起上訴後，該禁令的實施被暫時擱置。瑞典法院去年11月裁定，儘管上訴仍在處理中，但原定於2021年1月舉行的5G拍賣會可以繼續舉行。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，愛立信在中國5G市佔率為10％，且嚴重依賴中國分包商，尤其先前中國官員也威脅稱，若瑞典將華為及中興通訊排除在瑞典5G建設之外，勢必對愛立信在中國的業務產生負面影響。這就是傳出，愛立信已試圖聘請律師幫助華為在瑞典進行訴訟的原因之一。"},{"pid":"19dde56983cb9aa2d7e53d7be1d4ee7dd6b5a4e1","tid":2350794,"uid":31215,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />間諜"},{"pid":"66df0c9dca13bc0fd5ddb0c5f5a2e5daeb1cc370","tid":2350794,"uid":1524,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"而家共產黨就係利用自己國內市場嘅利潤威脅返你總公司嘅國家<br />\n<br />\n全世界都要經歷呢次陣痛"},{"pid":"678f8f94131790008e7a202d6291ae49b0269d63","tid":2350794,"uid":228955,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:16:41.000Z","msg":"應該佢收咗大筆錢"},{"pid":"121f52f25ea6fde7f568582365ded90d9354daf8","tid":2350794,"uid":336667,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"搬去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n封殺埋你"},{"pid":"7d5befc98e25877a516acf413fd847000bebcc52","tid":2350794,"uid":79410,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:20:08.000Z","msg":"今次真係六國論國際版<br />\n俾支那偷晒你D 技術. 你愛立信等食蕉啦"},{"pid":"e7fc5ec03852534f5f2f871ebe4ae878ce30f926","tid":2350794,"uid":335434,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"66df0c9dca13bc0fd5ddb0c5f5a2e5daeb1cc370","tid":2350794,"uid":1524,"like":175,"dislike":1,"score":174,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"而家共產黨就係利用自己國內市場嘅利潤威脅返你總公司嘅國家<br />\n<br />\n全世界都要經歷呢次陣痛"},"citedBy":0,"rep