"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"屌erricson nokia 華為 中興 全部奶共<br />\nCisco Juniper 有無做4G/5G  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6515d6ecedd8cdd93131a1cfcfefb7e13083df6","tid":2350794,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b945c31fc270b775e34a07a12a1f7299743251d5","tid":2350794,"uid":314083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e8aa473e1767010d02c8cd14d0f43fdc8dcb764","tid":2350794,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3399579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3399579&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb02aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=f75b863e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3399579&h=921f0676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3399579</a><br />\n<br />\n瑞典封殺中國華為及中興通訊參與5G網路建設，瑞典通訊大廠愛立信（Ericsson）CEO完全不挺。根據Pledge times引述瑞典《Dagens Nyheter》消息稱，愛立信CEO Borje Ekholm 寫了短信給瑞典商務部長，威脅除非解除對華為和中興的禁令，否則該公司不排除離開瑞典。商務部長則以「無法干預政府決定」強硬回絕。<br />\n<br />\n愛立信CEO Borje Ekholm 在短信中稱：「我仍然希望得到瑞典的幫助，以及我們在這個國家的存在能夠獲得重視。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6eCF5w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6eCF5w.png&h=aed199b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n商務部長Anna Hallberg則以「無法干預政府的決定」強硬回應，Anna Hallberg解釋，因為這一決定是由瑞典PTS（Police and Telecommunications Administration）根據安全部門和國防部門的建議作出的。<br />\n<br />\nBorje Ekholm又寫到：「嗨，Anna，我感謝您所做的工作，但現在看來，瑞典對愛立信來說是一個非常糟糕的國家。」<br />\n<br />\nAnna Hallberg 則向愛立信保證，「瑞典非常重視愛立信，但也會保持瑞典作為世界上最自由貿易國家之一的地位。」這一回應，沒想到又換來Borje Ekholm斥責，「當你處於我們的位置，你會完全明白為什麼歐洲的科技公司如此之少。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.bld.news/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/shutterstock_1629403723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.bld.news%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fshutterstock_1629403723.jpg&h=dfffa312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，去年10月，瑞典PTS宣布禁止華為及中興通訊參與瑞典5G建設後，在華為提起上訴後，該禁令的實施被暫時擱置。瑞典法院去年11月裁定，儘管上訴仍在處理中，但原定於2021年1月舉行的5G拍賣會可以繼續舉行。<br />\n<br />\n報導也指出，愛立信在中國5G市佔率為10％，且嚴重依賴中國分包商，尤其先前中國官員也威脅稱，若瑞典將華為及中興通訊排除在瑞典5G建設之外，勢必對愛立信在中國的業務產生負面影響。這就是傳出，愛立信已試圖聘請律師幫助華為在瑞典進行訴訟的原因之一。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"搞咁耐得半個美國醒咗"},{"pid":"b5937f451764a0b371ff2b5faa6a56c5672e67f8","tid":2350794,"uid":198088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b4a85b46076fd0fa7c9ed17a7cb821184199b6f","tid":2350794,"uid":45448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"屌erricson nokia 華為 中興 全部奶共<br />\nCisco Juniper 有無做4G/5G  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"CISCO 有份幫中共起網絡圍牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7cfdbdb35ab310a0e99323d8d84f04fbed3f40","tid":2350794,"uid":49853,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cbb6d59be3f4fb7030982a35b990af72f218f8a7","tid":2350794,"uid":34869,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"5d8a07a9d9115a659201479f552d0125ef6237d2","tid":2350794,"uid":235152,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"愛立信在中國5G市佔率為10％，且嚴重依賴中國分包商，<br />\n尤其先前中國官員也威脅稱，<br />\n若瑞典將華為及中興通訊排除在瑞典5G建設之外，<br />\n勢必對愛立信在中國的業務產生負面影響<br />\n<br />\n又俾中國渣住春袋,這就是全球化將所有外判到一個國家制造後果"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑<br />\n成件事明明係支那打橫黎<br />\n班商家佬個個掉轉槍口對自己國家<img sr